Not all their dishes are on the mark.
Their rice dishes are so-so, since they don't have com tam and use plain rice.
The bun is nice, but the pork they use is not quite what I'm use to.
They also have Vietnamese sandwiches, but again it is okay.
Oh, and one thing for vegetarians: if you get the vegetarian bun, do not use the sauce that comes with it because it's just good ol' Vietnamese fish sauce!
