...20 minutes later, I was still watching the same waitress clearing the same table that she had started clearing when we had walked in, and NO ONE from the waiting area had been seated yet.
Are you pho'king kidding me?!
I had half a mind to wrestle the dishcloth out of her hands and clear the tables myself.
